CHUNGHWA PICTURE June Sales Fall 37.36% (Table) : 2475 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T07:53:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/chunghwa-picture-june-sales-fall-37-36-table-2475-tt.html
CHUNGHWA PICTURE said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 37.36% to NT$4,305,912,000 from NT$6,873,878,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales           4,305,912        6,873,878   
YOY%             -37.36%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           29,482,957       39,228,441  
YOY%             -24.84% 
=================================================================
 